"content": "<h2>The cities of the plain of the River Jordan, chosen by Lot as a place of residence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:10-Gen13:12\">GEN 13:10–13:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Abraham rescues their inhabitants</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:1-Gen14:24\">GEN 14:1–14:24</a></p>\n<h3>Abraham prays for their inhabitants</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:17-Gen18:33\">GEN 18:17–18:33</a></p>\n<h3>Judgment on their sin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:1-Gen19:29\">GEN 19:1–19:29</a></p>\n<h2>The cities of the plain as symbols of sin and judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:23\">DEU 29:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:28-Luke17:29\">LUK 17:28–17:29</a></strong></p>",
